		<link>http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/chords/scotts-solo-bass-sessions-autumn-leaves.html</link>
		<comments>http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/chords/scotts-solo-bass-sessions-autumn-leaves.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 20 Oct 2014 12:16:12 +0000</pubDate>
