				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The one thing I get asked for over and over is videos of me playing live. So, I thought it was time to write some music, get a band together... and make some noise!</p>
<p>This is the first in a collection of singles I will be releasing over the upcoming months. These singles will be part of what I refer to as 'Project-Live'.</p>
<p>What's 'Project-Live' all about?...</p>
<p>None of the singles I release will have had any pre-rehearsals. The concept is to get musicians together that have never played together before, hand out some music, run through the piece a few times and then hit record.</p>
<p>You can also download this single totally free too. All I ask for in payment is... good karma! But if you <em>really</em> want to help me out, I'd love it if you passed this single on or forwarded a link to this video to anyone you thought might enjoy it!</p>
